HEADWORD: Tenaculum
<hw>Te*nac"u*lum</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
L. <plw>Tenacula</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>; E. <plw>Tenaculums</plw>
